metadata.name: POPSTEAK Member
metadata.description:
This token represents your ownership of membership to the Popsteak community and restaurant.

As a Popsteak member, you will have access to our cocktail lounge, restaurant and private events. By holding a token for more than a year, you become a member of the Popsteak family and gain access to the community's profit pool. 20% of both royalties and restaurant profits are allocated to this pool, and members are given an opportunity to claim their share of rewards annually.

All food & beverage costs are paid at your time of visit and are not included in the token price.

After purchasing on OpenSea, please create a member profile at https://popsteak.com and connect your wallet to verify ownership of your token. This is necessary for you to make reservations and see upcoming events.
